    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\text{Ta có: } \\sin\\alpha = \\frac{|\\overrightarrow{MA} \\cdot \\vec{n}|}{|\\overrightarrow{MA}| \\cdot |\\vec{n}|} = \\frac{|-3 \\cdot (-2) + 4 \\cdot (-21) + 3 \\cdot (-26)|}{\\sqrt{(-3)^2 + 4^2 + 3^2} \\cdot \\sqrt{(-2)^2 + (-21)^2 + (-26)^2}} = \\frac{156}{\\sqrt{38114}} \\Rightarrow \\alpha \\approx 53^{\\circ}\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
