      1145,
      1269,
      1332
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\begin{aligned} \\text{Khi đó: } \\sin\\beta &= \\frac{|\\overrightarrow{NA} \\cdot \\vec{n}|}{|\\overrightarrow{NA}| \\cdot |\\vec{n}|} = \\frac{|5 \\cdot (-2) + 2 \\cdot (-21) + 4 \\cdot (-26)|}{\\sqrt{5^2 + 2^2 + 4^2} \\cdot \\sqrt{(-2)^2 + (-21)^2 + (-26)^2}} = \\frac{156}{\\sqrt{50445}} \\Rightarrow \\beta \\approx 44^{\\circ} \\\\ \\Rightarrow a = 53; b = 44 \\Rightarrow T = a + b = 97 \\end{aligned}\n$$"
